marketing: Shell Gadus S5 V150XKD 0/00 is part of Shell’s comprehensive range of multi-purpose mining and construction equipment greases, which offers protection from sustained heavy duty operations and shock loads in all climates and seasons. This advanced, fully-synthetic grease offers excellent mobility even in Arctic winter conditions, for reliable delivery through central lubrication systems. Shell Gadus S5 V150XKD 0/00 is formulated to excellent all-round performance, balancing mobility, load-carrying capability and long effective life in hostile operating conditions.
